},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://youtu.be/_RlMkDgILM4"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第五套 肩帶運動"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://youtu.be/hcBJKlfsG4I"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第六套 核心運動"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://youtu.be/K6JUMXvkPNQ"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第七套 下肢運動"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://youtu.be/GKjDnTIeSW4"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第八套 肩帶伸展"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://youtu.be/iisYN1qq_fk"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第九套 核心伸展"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://youtu.be/jJjpgNkSXcU"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第十套 下肢伸展"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"體適能運動"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"體適能運動"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善肌力的運動:以阻力訓練(重量訓練)為主,可以分為徒手訓練、器械訓練或自由重量三大類,概念上就是對要訓練的肌群逐步增加負重,來改善肌肉量和動作表現。重量訓練依據訓練法的不同,可以分別提升爆發力、肌力、肌肉量或肌耐力,建議由專業教練指導,避免運動傷害。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善柔軟度的運動:以伸展運動為主,常被稱做拉筋,最為人熟知的就是瑜珈,但任何幫助肌肉拉伸延展的運動都算。可以分為動態伸展和靜態伸展,動態伸展有助於運動前暖身,增加關節活動度,也可以預防運動傷害,靜態伸展適合安排在運動後,將運動時收縮的肌肉拉回原本的長度,平常即使沒有從事運動,也可以透過伸展運動來舒緩長期久坐不動產生的緊繃不適。搭配正確的運動按摩,或震動訓練,都有助於改善柔軟度。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"心肺適能的運動:以有氧運動為主,例如快走、慢跑、自行車、游泳、一般而言,心肺耐力較佳的人,安靜時休息心跳比較慢,運動後心較快。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善平衡感的運動:維持平衡除了要具備基本肌力之外,身體的本體感覺。本體感覺可以透過動作訓練來強化,這類運動通常稱為功能於年長者預防跌倒是不可或缺的。利用在水中運動(水適能),也可以改善平衡感。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"體適能運動範例"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  "},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n      "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":" https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=3Pr7E5IMAeU&list=UUMX_-z6mC8L-hbFTsHoloFw&index=35"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上肢訓線-扶竿伏地挺身"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n      "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?app=desktop&v=TiZzaeKjH8o&list=UUMX_-z6mC8L-hbFTsHoloFw&index=40"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"下肢訓練-高抬腿"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n      "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?app=desktop&v=Y3if5Q_eWbM&list=UUMX_-z6mC8L-hbFTsHoloFw&index=45"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上肢訓練-弹力帶房上舉"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n      "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?app=desktop&v=iXXy0x6tA9E&list=UUMX_-z6mC8L-hbFTsHoloFw&index=20"},"children":[{"type":"te